{
  "texts": [
    "Simultaneously, the constructed MMRS-1M dataset contains various visual modalities.",
    "C. Remote Sensing DatasetsRS datasets are the core and foundation of RS intelligent interpretation models.",
    "Currently, RS datasets mainly focus on classification, detection, segmentation, image captioning, and VQA tasks.",
    "For classification, commonly used datasets include AID [41], EuroSAT [42], NWPU-RESISC45 [43], UCMerced LandUse [44], and WHU-RS19 [45].",
    "For detection, optical datasets like DIOR [46], DOTA [47], FAIR1M [48], HRRSD [49], NWPUVHR10 [50], and SAR datasets like AIR-SARShip-2.0 [51], HRSID [52], and SSDD [53] are used to train expert models."
  ]
}